        <h2>Pytanie 5:</h2>
        <p>Wzór Bayesa wykorzystywany w klasyfikatorze naiwnego Bayesa ma postać:</p>
        <input type="checkbox" id="q5a" name="q5" value="A">
        <label for="q5a">A) \(P(Y = y |X = x) = \frac{P(X = x |Y = y)P(Y = y)}{P(X = x)}\)</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="q5b" name="q5" value="B">
        <label for="q5b">B) \(P(Y = y |X = x) = P(X = x |Y = y)P(Y = y)\)</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="q5c" name="q5" value="C">
        <label for="q5c">C) \(P(X = x |Y = y) = \frac{P(Y = y |X = x)P(X = x)}{P(Y = y)}\)</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="q5d" name="q5" value="D">
        <label for="q5d">D) \(P(X = x |Y = y) = P(Y = y |X = x)P(X = x)\)</label><br>
        
